    <h1 style="color: var(--tf-purple-bright); margin-bottom: 16px;">╔══════════════════════════╗</h1>
    <h1 style="color: var(--tf-purple-bright);">║   T-NET BBS v3.0 (3D)   ║</h1>
    <h1 style="color: var(--tf-purple-bright); margin-bottom: 16px;">╚══════════════════════════╝</h1>
    <p>Welcome to the 3D desk scene test.</p>
    <p style="margin-top: 8px;">The terminal content renders here, overlaid on the 3D monitor screen.</p>
    <br />
    <p style="color: var(--tf-cyan);">SysOp: Todd LeBaron</p>
    <p style="color: var(--tf-cyan);">Location: Scottsdale, AZ</p>
  </div>
</BBS3D>
